2e:["$","div",null,{"className":"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between gap-6","children":[["$","$L5",null,{"href":"/posts/sec021","className":"flex gap-2 hover:opacity-75 items-start","children":[["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"2","strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"inline-block flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":[["$","path",null,{"d":"M0 0h24v24H0z","stroke":"none"}],["$","path",null,{"d":"M15 6l-6 6l6 6"}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"min-w-0","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"block text-sm text-foreground/70","children":"上一篇"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-accent/85","children":"安全加固与基线核查"}]]}]]}],["$","$L5",null,{"href":"/posts/sec019","className":"flex gap-2 hover:opacity-75 items-start justify-end text-right ml-auto","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"min-w-0","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"block text-sm text-foreground/70","children":"下一篇"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-accent/85","children":"Linux应急响应实战"}]]}],["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":"2","strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"inline-block flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5","children":[["$","path",null,{"d":"M0 0h24v24H0z","stroke":"none"}],["$","path",null,{"d":"M9 6l6 6l-6 6"}]]}]]}]]}]
25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：负责漏洞治理、扫描平台与风险优先级管理的安全运营同学。\n阅读前提：了解 CVE、补丁和基本资产分类。\n核心收获：把漏洞扫描结果转成可执行的评估、分级与修复流程。\n说明：扫描器能力与插件库更新频繁，具体操作请结合当前版本界面与官方文档。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"漏洞是网络安全的阿喀琉斯之踵。即使拥有完善的安全策略和应急响应能力，如果系统中存在未修复的已知漏洞，攻击者依然可以轻松突破防线。漏洞扫描与风险评估是安全运营中不可或缺的环节，它帮助组织主动发现和修复安全弱点，将被动防御转化为主动治理。本文将深入讲解漏洞管理体系、CVSS 评分标准，并以 Nessus 和 OpenVAS(GVM) 两大扫描平台为例，展示漏洞扫描的完整实战流程。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"漏洞管理生命周期","children":["漏洞管理生命周期",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#漏洞管理生命周期","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"漏洞管理不是一次性的扫描活动，而是一个持续循环的过程。业界公认的漏洞管理生命周期包含以下阶段："}],"\n",["$","ol",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"资产发现（Asset Discovery）"}],"：识别和清点组织的所有 IT 资产，包括服务器、终端、网络设备、云资源和应用程序"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"漏洞扫描（Vulnerability Scanning）"}],"：使用自动化工具对资产进行扫描，识别已知漏洞和配置缺陷"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"漏洞评估（Vulnerability Assessment）"}],"：对扫描结果进行分析和验证，评估漏洞的真实风险等级"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"优先级排序（Prioritization）"}],"：结合资产重要性、漏洞严重程度和可利用性，确定修复优先级"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"漏洞修复（Remediation）"}],"：实施补丁安装、配置修改或其他缓解措施"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"验证复查（Verification）"}],"：重新扫描确认漏洞已被成功修复"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"报告与度量（Reporting & Metrics）"}],"：生成管理报告，跟踪漏洞修复趋势和关键指标（MTTR、漏洞密度等）"]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"这个循环应当以固定的频率持续运转——高安全要求的环境建议每周扫描，一般环境至少每月一次。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"cvss-评分体系详解","children":["CVSS 评分体系详解",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#cvss-评分体系详解","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"通用漏洞评分系统（Common Vulnerability Scoring System, CVSS）是业界标准的漏洞严重程度量化方法。当前最新版本为 CVSS v3.1（CVSS v4.0 已发布但尚未完全普及）。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"cvss-v31-评分维度","children":["CVSS v3.1 评分维度",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#cvss-v31-评分维度","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"基础指标组（Base Metrics）："}]," 描述漏洞本身的固有特征"]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"指标"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"含义"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"取值示例"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Attack Vector (AV)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"攻击向量"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Network / Adjacent / Local / Physical"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Attack Complexity (AC)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"攻击复杂度"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Low / High"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Privileges Required (PR)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"所需权限"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"None / Low / High"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"User Interaction (UI)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"用户交互"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"None / Required"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Scope (S)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"影响范围"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Unchanged / Changed"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Confidentiality (C)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"机密性影响"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"None / Low / High"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Integrity (I)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"完整性影响"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"None / Low / High"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":"Availability (A)"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"可用性影响"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"None / Low / High"}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"时间指标组（Temporal Metrics）："}]," 随时间变化的属性"]}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"Exploit Code Maturity：是否已有成熟的利用工具"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"Remediation Level：是否有官方补丁或缓解方案"}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"Report Confidence：漏洞信息的可信程度"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"环境指标组（Environmental Metrics）："}]," 根据组织自身环境调整"]}],"\n",["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":"允许根据资产在组织中的重要程度调整最终评分"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"cvss-评分等级","children":["CVSS 评分等级",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#cvss-评分等级","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L30","\n","$L31","\n","$L32","\n","$L33","\n","$L34","\n","$L35","\n","$L36","\n","$L37","\n","$L38","\n","$L39","\n","$L3a","\n","$L3b","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L4d","\n","$L4e","\n","$L4f","\n","$L50","\n","$L51","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L52","\n","$L53","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L54","\n","$L55","\n","$L56","\n","$L57","\n","$L58","\n","$L59","\n","$L5a","\n","$L5b","\n","$L5c","\n","$L5d","\n","$L5e"]
