33:["$","ul",null,{"children":["\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"CVE（Common Vulnerabilities and Exposures）"}],"：通用漏洞披露标识。每个已公开的安全漏洞会被分配一个唯一的 CVE ID，格式如 ",["$","code",null,{"children":"CVE-2024-12345"}],"。由 MITRE 组织维护。"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"CWE（Common Weakness Enumeration）"}],"：通用缺陷枚举。对软件安全弱点的分类体系，描述漏洞的根本原因类型，如 CWE-79（XSS）、CWE-89（SQL 注入）。用于理解漏洞的本质。"]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"children":"NVD（National Vulnerability Database）"}],"：美国国家漏洞数据库。由 NIST 维护，在 CVE 基础上增加了 CVSS 评分、受影响产品版本（CPE）、修复建议等丰富信息。"]}],"\n"]}]
